<p> I currently hold a Junior Research Fellowship at Magdalen College, Oxford. My DPhil thesis is on vagueness and on issues relating to the semantic paradoxes. I am also working on topics in metaphysics, epistemology, the philosophy of language, philosophical logic and the philosophy of mathematics.</p>

